nodes.text: Nicolas Cantu (born September 8, 2003) is an American child actor. He voiced the character "Diego" in the children's television program Dora and Friends: Into the City!. Cantu has also played roles in the movie The Impossible Joy and the animated television series Hey Arnold!.He is the middle child in a family with three sibilings.
He is the voice actor of Rowan Freemaker, one of the four main protagonists of LEGO Star Wars: The Freemaker Adventures.
